Feature: Glisseo

    Causes the steps on a stairway to flatten and form a ramp or slide.

    Pronunciation:
        /ˈɡlɪsiː.oʊ/ GLIS-ee-oh or /ɡlɪˈseɪ.oʊ/ gli-SAY-oh
    Seen/mentioned:
        Used by Hermione to escape from pursuing Death Eaters in Deathly
        Hallows. Used on the girls' dormitory to ensure that boys cannot enter.
